{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "拉萨依旧平静，阳光和小方回到圣城，却发现卜鹰势力已瓦解。鹰记商号被卫天鹏夺取，伙计全换新人。卜鹰的庄院被一场大火烧成废墟，数百人无一幸免。噶伦大喇嘛的弟子阿苏前来清理火场，告诉阳光只找到十三坛骨灰，无一活口。阿苏暗示有内应参与，且知道一个关于卜鹰、班察巴那和波娃三人身世的秘密，但话未说完就被阴灵毒杀。阳光坚信卜鹰仍活着，引用\"蝮蛇螫手，壮士断腕\"之理，与小方决心寻找卜鹰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "这里好像什么事都没发生过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "如果那些人已经来了，已经有了行动，这里一定变得很乱了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "每次有事发生时，卜鹰都会派人在城外巡逻示警。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "可是现在这附近连一个我们的人都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "有些事件虽然看不见也听不见，却还是不能否定它的存在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "有时它甚至远比能够看得见也听得见的更真实，也存在得更久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "朱云看见你的时候，样子说不定会有点怪怪的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "你不要理他就好了，不管他怎么样对你，你最好都假装没看见。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "listener_name": "京片子伙计",
      "text": "我什么都不买。我是来找人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "京片子伙计",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "找哪位？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "listener_name": "京片子伙计",
      "text": "我找朱云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "京片子伙计",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "我们这儿没听说有这么样一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "listener_name": "京片子伙计",
      "text": "我看你一定是新来的。你来了多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "京片子伙计",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "才三天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "listener_name": "京片子伙计",
      "text": "你知不知道这里的老板是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "京片子伙计",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "做伙计的人，如果连老板是谁都不知道，岂非是糊涂虫？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji_jing_pian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "京片子伙计",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "这儿的老板姓卫，不是燕赵韩魏的魏，是天津卫的卫，叫卫天鹏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "我认得你。你是噶伦大喇嘛的弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "是！我叫阿苏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "是他叫你来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "三天前我就已来过。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "那时火已熄了，我来清理火场。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "你找到了什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "在劫难逃，天意难测，我来时这里已经什么都没有了，什么都被烧光了，我只找到了一点骨灰。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "骨灰？是谁的骨灰？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "是谁的骨灰？是谁的骨灰？……这里也有我的族人，我的朋友，这三天里我日日夜夜都在找，我也想知道那是谁的骨灰，只可惜每个人的尸骨都已成灰，还有谁能分辨得出？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "每个人？每个人是什么意思？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "你知不知道这里本来一共有多少人？你说每个人，难道是说他们全都——？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "不会的，绝不会。这里一定还有人活着，一定还有，你只要找到一个，就可以问出别的人在哪里了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "难道你连一个人都没有找到？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "没有。我连一个活着的人都没有找到。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "起火的那天晚上，这里究竟发生了什么事？究竟是谁放的火？恐怕永远都没有人能够说出真相来了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "没有人能说出真相？难道你还猜不到谁是凶手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "你知道凶手是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "我当然知道。卫天鹏、胡大掌柜、风叟月婆、阴灵，这些人都是凶手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "你认为就凭这些人，就能将卜鹰、朱云、严正刚、宋老夫子，和这里的数百战士在一夕之间一网打尽？不留一个活口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "就凭这些人，恐怕还办不到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "你认为还有谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "还有内应！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "内应？你认为这里也有他们埋伏的奸细？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "你们能够派奸细埋伏在他们的组织里，他们为什么不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "波娃呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "那天晚上，波娃也到这里来了。她说她一定要来见卜鹰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "起火的时候，她也在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "现在她人呢？是死是活？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "难道你怀疑她已经做了对方的奸细？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "这次你错了。奸细绝不是波娃！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "你怎么能确定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "因为……因为我在无意间发现了一个秘密。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_a_su",
      "listener_name": "阿苏",
      "text": "什么秘密？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_su",
      "speaker_name": "阿苏",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "有关卜鹰、班察巴那、和波娃三个人之间的秘密，有关他们的身世和……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "我们走。我们去找卜鹰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "你能找得到他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "只要他不死，我就能找得到。他一定不会死的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "如果他还没有死，怎么能抛得下这些事，自己却一走了之？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "蝮蛇螫手，壮士断腕。到了必要时，什么事他都能抛得下，什么事他都可以牺牲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "因为他要活下去，无论活得多艰苦，他都要活下去，因为他还要重建他的家园，还要歼灭他的仇敌，所以他能走，不能死！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "listener_name": "小方",
      "text": "你应该明白，死有时远比活容易得多，有人虽然宁可选择比较容易的一条路走，宁可一死了之，他却绝不是这种人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "listener_name": "阳光",
      "text": "是的，我明白。他一定还活着，一定不会死的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
